original_title: Ramani Gomes, President, Inner Wheel Club, Colombo Central
original_body_lines: Inner Wheel Club of Colombo Central held its installation ceremony for the newly elected President of the Club Ms. Ramani Gomes for the year 2024/2025 at the Automobile Association of Ceylon(AAC) Auditorium on 17th July.
